                    </li>
                    <li>Foodready.net offers Free advertising online and in the media.</li>
                    <li>Using foodready.net will help you reach new markets.</li>
                    <li>
                        Orders placed through foodready.net are clearly printed, eliminating errors due to misinterpretation
                        or handwriting illegibility.
                    </li>
                    <li>No misunderstanding, no miscommunications.</li>
                    <li>
                        Foodready.net has Millions of registered users and our user bank is growing every day. Get
